Saipem May Team Up With United Shipbuilding in Russia, Overseas

-- B y   S t e p h e n   B i e r m a n
-- 
2011-09-23T10:48:17Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-09-23/saipem-may-team-up-with-united-shipbuilding-in-russia-overseas.html
Saipem SpA (SPM) , the Italian oilfield
services provider whose largest shareholder is  Eni SpA (ENI) , may
collaborate with Moscow-based United Shipbuilding Corp. on
projects in Russia and abroad.  The companies signed an agreement to study the possibility
of a joint venture, Saipem said today in a statement on its
 website .  To contact the reporter on this story:
Stephen Bierman in Moscow at 
 sbierman1@bloomberg.net .  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Will Kennedy at   wkennedy3@bloomberg.net . 